---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About | Knowledge Base"
  description="Learn more about Jon Carlsen and this knowledge base"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1
        class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 sm:text-4xl fade-in"
      >
        About Me
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300 slide-up">
        Welcome to my personal knowledge repository
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div
          class="aspect-square rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-800 overflow-hidden relative"
        >
          <!-- Replace initials with actual profile image -->
          <img
            src="/tech-leadership/profilepicture.jpg"
            alt="Jon Carlsen"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 prose dark:prose-dark prose-lg">
        <h2>Hello, I'm Jon Carlsen</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a highly analytical and technically astute professional with an
          exceptional talent for planning and coordinating engineering
          activities to improve overall business efficiency. With a successful
          background in leading product strategy and technology initiatives, I
          specialize in developing and implementing innovative solutions that
          drive business growth, enhance customer experience, and increase
          operational efficiency.
        </p>
        <p>
          With over 17 years of experience in the tech industry, I've developed
          expertise in various domains including software development, team
          leadership, and technical architecture. I'm passionate about building
          and leading high-performing teams, fostering a culture of innovation,
          collaboration, and continuous improvement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Skills section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-6"
      >
        Skills & Expertise
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div
          class="bg-white dark:bg-primary-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800"
        >
          <h3
            class="font-semibold text-lg text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-2"
          >
            Technical Leadership
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300">
            Leading engineering teams, technical strategy, and architecture
            implementation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white dark:bg-primary-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800"
        >
          <h3
            class="font-semibold text-lg text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-2"
          >
            Cloud & Platform
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300">
            Cloud-native architecture, Kubernetes, microservices, and platform
            engineering.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white dark:bg-primary-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800"
        >
          <h3
            class="font-semibold text-lg text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-2"
          >
            Agile & DevOps
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-300">
            Implementing agile methodologies, continuous delivery, and DevOps
            practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white dark:bg-primary-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-800"
        >
          <h3
            class="font-semibold text-lg text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-2"
